rformance and capability relative to approved procedures, standards and practices is reviewed on an ongoing basis and is a primary factor considered in design and installation of all new and improved process equipment. The Arclin Springfield site has and continues to invest in improved technology and automated process control systems to provide enhanced process safety and production unit performance.





Summary of Changes;

There have been no significant plant changes over the past 5-years that would modify the worst case or alternate case release scenarios. No changes have been made that increases production capacity or operating temperatures or pressures that could reduce equipment reliability.
